        <heading>Firefighters moving from one city to another</heading>
        <content>
          <p>  ยง 15. Firefighters moving from one city to another. The firefighters\nof the different cities of this state, in case of removal from one city\nto another, shall be allowed the time which they have served as such\nfirefighters in the city they left, in the city to which they have\nremoved, upon producing a certificate of such service, signed by the\nchief of the city so left, and being appointed firefighters in the city\nto which they have removed.\n</p>
        </content>
      </section>
